<item>
            <title>[LU-19946] Create an --mmp specific option for mkfs.lustre</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19946</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Watching an AI hallucinate the --mmp option for mkfs.lustre got me thinking that this might be a useful thing to have. Right now we automatically enable MMP if mkfsoptions=&quot;-O MMP&quot; etc. is specified but this may not be desirable in all cases (such as testing, etc).&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As a result I&apos;m proposing we simplify this with this --mmp or --MMP to enable / disable.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
